content: madjin: Focused on enhancing content delivery for the `elizaos/elizaos.github.io` project by implementing a new RSS feed feature. They merged two significant PRs to add the feed endpoint (#172) and then fix its URL configuration (#175), with code changes primarily split between feature work and bug fixes. Madjin also planned for future work by creating several issues, including a blocker for a Next.js upgrade (#176) and a feature request for fuzzy search (#174).
